;; blocks and links:
;;
;; 0. A unified interface, the ‘defblock’ macro, for making new block and link types.
;;
;; 1. Colours: Regions of text and inline text can be coloured using 19 colours;
;;  easily extendable; below is an example.
;;
;;             #+begin_red org
